text: Ann Cusack (born May 22, 1961) is an American actress. She was born in New York City. Cusack is the sister of actors John Cusack and Joan Cusack. Cusack is known for her comedy roles in A League of Their Own (1992), Multiplicity (1996) and The Informant!
